                android:text="If you are a teenager or a teenagerâ€™s parent,\nJoin our xxxxx program to xxxxxx\nIf you are a college student,\nJoin our xxxxx program to xxxxxx\nIf you are a university professor or academic researcher,\nJoin our xxxxx program to xxxxxx\nIf you are a professional working in the STEMM field,\nJoin our xxxxx program to xxxxxx\nIf you are a layman new to the STEMM field,\nJoin our xxxxx program to xxxxxx">
